---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Palm Springs Wedding Invitations & Save the Dates | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Custom Palm Springs wedding invitations and save the dates inspired by desert weddings, mid-century modern design, retro colors, and California celebrations.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Palm Springs Wedding Invitations & Save the Dates</h1>

    <p>
      Custom wedding invitation suites inspired by Palm Springs style, desert weddings,
      mid-century modern design, colorful retro details, and elevated California celebrations.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning a stylish resort wedding, a modern desert celebration,
      or a colorful Palm Springs wedding weekend, your stationery should set the tone
      from the very first save the date.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by Palm Springs Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      Palm Springs weddings are known for their unique mix of desert beauty, modern
      architecture, boutique hotels, poolside celebrations, bold colors, and relaxed
      luxury.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our Palm Springs wedding invitations can be designed to reflect your venue,
      wedding colors, typography preferences, and overall wedding aesthetic.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Palm Springs Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Palm Springs wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Palm Springs save the dates</li>
      <li>Mid-century modern wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Desert wedding invitation suites</li>
      <li>Retro wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Colorful modern wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Minimalist Palm Springs invitations</li>
      <li>California destination wedding invitations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Stylish Wedding Weekends</h2>

    <p>
      Palm Springs is a popular destination for wedding weekends, welcome parties,
      poolside gatherings, rehearsal dinners, ceremonies, receptions, and farewell brunches.
    </p>

    <p>
      We can create cohesive stationery for the full celebration, including save the dates,
      wedding invitations, RSVP cards, details cards, itinerary cards, welcome signage,
      menus, seating charts, and day-of paper goods.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Palm Springs Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for a fully custom invitation suite? We can design Palm Springs wedding
      stationery that feels personal to your venue, your guests, and your celebration.
    </p>

    <p>
      From clean and minimal to bold, colorful, retro, or mid-century inspired, each design
      can be customized to match your wedding vision.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Do you design Palm Springs save the dates?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. We can create custom save the dates for Palm Springs weddings, destination
      wedding weekends, and California desert celebrations.
    </p>

    <h3>Can the invitations include mid-century modern design?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Palm Springs invitations can include retro typography, geometric layouts,
      vintage-inspired colors, modern architecture details, and other mid-century design elements.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching signage, menus, seating charts, escort cards, and other wedding day
      paper goods can be designed to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer printed and digital invitations?</h3>
    <p>
      We offer both digital invitation designs and professionally printed wedding stationery.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
